anding of IT hardware.", "short_description": "Virtual TechLab is the leading virtual learning environment that is revolutionizing IT hardware education. "}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "903131914935432", "locale": "nl_NL", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Virtual Techlab", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Virtual Techlab biedt de unieke kans om onbeperkt te kunnen oefenen met het vakkundig assembleren van IT-componenten in een virtuele omgeving. De virtuele omgeving maakt het mogelijk om te kunnen leren zonder de beperkingen die traditionele leermethodes met zich meebrengen, zoals beperkte budgetten, tijd en hardware. Je kunt op je eigen tempo leren, fouten maken zonder gevolgen en je begrip van IT-hardware verdiepen.", "short_description": "Virtual TechLab, d\u00e9 toonaangevende virtuele leeromgeving die het IT-hardware onderwijs revolutioneert. "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.changefied.nl/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.changefied.nl/en/algemene-voorwaarden", "publisher_name": "Changefied", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.changefied.nl/en/virtual-techlab", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "879473995923081"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["nl"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "25265931756353917"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUB